        <item>
            <title>HUAWEI Pura 70 突发推出，运行 HarmonyOS 4.2、1/1.3 吋感光元件主相机</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/18/huawei-pura-70/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=huawei-pura-70</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/18/huawei-pura-70/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 05:30:26 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pura 70]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pura 70 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pura 70 Ultra]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[华为]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1229999</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>华为在未有开发布会的情况下，今（18 日）突然推出「HUAWEI Pura 70 系列，先锋计划」，Pura 70、70 Pro、70 Pro+、70 Ultra 四个机款将会登场，售价由 5,499 人民币（约 6,070 <span data-mid="/m/02nb4kq" data-name="港元">港元</span>）起。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1230004 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-4-694x197.png" alt="" width="694" height="197" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-4-694x197.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-4.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1230001 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-1-694x199.png" alt="" width="694" height="199" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-1-694x199.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-1.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1230002 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-2-694x198.png" alt="" width="694" height="198" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-2-694x198.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-2.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1230003 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-3-694x198.png" alt="" width="694" height="198" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-3-694x198.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-3.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲华为推出 Pura 70、Pura 70 Pro、Pura 70 Pro+ 及 Pura 70 Ultra，售价由 5,499 人民币（约 6,070 <span data-mid="/m/02nb4kq" data-name="港元">港元</span>）起。</p><p>华为 Pura 70、Pura 70 Pro、Pura 70 Pro+ 及 Pura 70 Ultra 的设计独特，圆角三角形的相机外观具辨识度。Ultra 型号拥有星芒底纹，而 Pro+ 亦有光织格纹。Pura 70 使用 6.6 吋的 OLED 萤幕，其余三机则是 6.8 吋，四部新机的解析度及刷新率均有 FHD+ 和 120Hz。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1230009 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-8-655x580.png" alt="" width="655" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-8-655x580.png 655w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-8.png 1016w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 655px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Ultra 型号拥有星芒底纹</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1230007 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-6-688x580.png" alt="" width="688" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-6-688x580.png 688w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-6.png 1048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 688px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Pro+ 亦有光织格纹</p><p>Pura 70 Ultra 坐拥 4000 万像素 f/2.2 光圈超广角相机及 5000 万像素 f/2.1 光圈，OIS 光学防手震超聚光微距长焦相机，可处理 200X 数码变焦拍摄，并使用了 1 吋感光元件，支援感光元件移位防震功能。 f/1.6-f/4.0 光圈镜头首次加入旋转伸缩镜头结构，使用时会出现机械声音。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1230008 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-7-643x580.png" alt="" width="643" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-7-643x580.png 643w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/screenshot20240418at-7.png 997w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 643px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Pura 70 Ultra 坐拥 4000 万像素 f/2.2 光圈超广角相机及 5000 万像素 f/2.1 光圈，OIS 光学防手震超聚光微距长焦相机</p><p>华为 Pura 70、Pura 70 Pro、Pura 70 Pro+ 及 Pura 70 Ultra，定价分别为 5,499 人民币（约 6,070 <span data-mid="/m/02nb4kq" data-name="港元">港元</span>）、6,499 人民币（约 7,173 港元）、7,999 人民币（约 8,656 <span data-mid="/m/02nb4kq" data-name="港元">港元</span>）及 9,999 人民币（约 10,820 <span data-mid="/m/02nb4kq" data-name="港元">港元</span>）。Pro 和 Ultra 即日起在中国开卖，其余两款则要等到 4 月 22 日才有售。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.vmall.com/product/10086821546239.html">Vmall</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/15/matebook-x-pro/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">华为 AI 手提电脑配备 Intel 先进晶片，美国议员表示不可接受</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/13/richard-yu-huawei-2/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">华为余承东自主不再讲「遥遥领先」   中国网民表示不习惯</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/10/toyota-huawei-monenta-sign-agreement/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">丰田、华为、Momenta 合作，研发智能驾驶辅助系统</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/18/huawei-pura-70/mobile-phone/">HUAWEI Pura 70 突发推出，运行 HarmonyOS 4.2、1/1.3 吋感光元件主相机</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
