        </item>
        <item>
            <title>新 X 用户等 3 个月才可发文，两国试新制度打击 AI 假帐户</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/x-need-to-pay-to-post/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=x-need-to-pay-to-post</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/x-need-to-pay-to-post/life-tech/social-network/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 12:30:49 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交网络]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Elon Musk]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Twitter]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[x]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1229946</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>AI 发展一日千里，为大家生活带来方便之余，亦带来不少资讯安全问题。Elon Musk 近日表示， X 拟在纽西兰及菲律宾测试新收费制度，用户如申请帐户后要立即发文需要缴付 1 美元（约港币 7.8 元），或者等候 3 个月方能够发文。</p><p>Elon Musk 在 X 证实将会对新用户征费。Elon Musk 指，现今 AI 技术日益先进，甚至破解了以往「机械人认证」，因此将会征收「小额费用」。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Unfortunately, a small fee for new user write access is the only way to curb the relentless onslaught of bots. </p><p>Current AI (and troll farms) can pass 「are you a bot」 with ease.</p><p>&mdash; Elon Musk (@elonmusk) <a href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1779930065469383166?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">April 15, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>Elon Musk 另外回复指，用户亦可选择不付费，但开设帐户头 3 个月没有发文权限，仅能够浏览帖文，要等 3 个月期限后方能够发文及回复。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">That is way harder than paying a tiny fee. </p><p>This is only for new users. They will be able to do write actions for free after 3 months.</p><p>&mdash; Elon Musk (@elonmusk) <a href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1779939517278957714?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">April 15, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2023/jul/31/x-sign-lights-san-francisco-twitter-office-removed">The Guardian</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.cool3c.com/article/214120">Cool3c</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/15/vivo-x-fold3-pro-china-version-review/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】vivo X Fold3 Pro 国行，外形　手感　铰位　功能　主副屏幕　相机　效能开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/14/xs-premium-users-can-no-longer-hide-their-blue-checks/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">X 将移除隐藏「蓝剔」功能　Elon Musk 接管 Twitter 时曾引起争议</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/11/microsoft-ai-pc-event-20-may/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Microsoft 下月举办 AI PC 活动，力推 Snapdragon X Elite 笔电</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/x-need-to-pay-to-post/life-tech/social-network/">新 X 用户等 3 个月才可发文，两国试新制度打击 AI 假帐户</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/x-need-to-pay-to-post/life-tech/social-network/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
