            <title>疑有 DSE 监考员小红书泄答题簿，考评局：会报警处理</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/dse-xiaohongshu-leakage/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=dse-xiaohongshu-leakage</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/dse-xiaohongshu-leakage/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 10:30:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[dse]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小红书]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1229940</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>上周六（13 日）DSE 英文聆听已经开考，网上流传有监考人员将相关试卷的试题答题库上传至中国社交平台「小红书」。据《明报》引述考评局指，当局正严肃跟进相关事件，将会报警处理。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229942" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/436166096_1221405133-579x580.jpg" alt="" width="579" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/436166096_1221405133-579x580.jpg 579w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/436166096_1221405133.jpg 899w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/436166096_1221405133-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 579px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/photo/?fbid=122140513370146904&amp;set=pcb.122140513436146904">教育刺针</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229943" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/437536834_1221405133-579x580.jpg" alt="" width="579" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/437536834_1221405133-579x580.jpg 579w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/437536834_1221405133.jpg 899w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/437536834_1221405133-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 579px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/photo/?fbid=122140513370146904&amp;set=pcb.122140513436146904">教育刺针</a></p><p>Facebook 专页「教育刺针」日前发文指，有人将考生不可携带离场的 question-answer book （试题答题簿，考生必须交回且不可携带离开）内容上传至小红书。涉事答题簿为本年度 DSE 英文聆听卷答题簿，小红书用户「Ms.Lucy」将该空白答题簿打上「Ms.Lucy」水印后上传至小红书，并附以评语：「监考结束，大家进来看看考的怎样？」。小红书用户「Ms.Lucy」自称学历树仁本科，于港大就读硕士，现职中学中文教师。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229941" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/437387182_1221405133-579x580.jpg" alt="" width="579" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/437387182_1221405133-579x580.jpg 579w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/437387182_1221405133.jpg 898w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/437387182_1221405133-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 579px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/photo/?fbid=122140513370146904&amp;set=pcb.122140513436146904">教育刺针</a></p><p>《明报》就事件查询考评局，考评局回复指会严肃跟进未经许可转载试题一事，将会交由警方处理，如有考务人员违反保密规定，将会按照规定采取行动。据《明报》引述《香港考试及评核局条例》指，未经局方批准，不得将试题内容转载或刊登。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20240417/s00002/1713291913694/">明报</a>、<a href="https://www.facebook.com/photo/?fbid=122140513370146904&amp;set=pcb.122140513436146904">教育刺针</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/12/dse-2/software/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">DSE 监考员仍未能登入「监考易」　今日续需人手点名</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/11/dse/software/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">DSE「监考易」App 失灵　监考员须改用人手核对考生身份</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/dse-xiaohongshu-leakage/fun-tech/">疑有 DSE 监考员小红书泄答题簿，考评局：会报警处理</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
